column1:
Para gerar um arquivo CSV com 500 comandos, utilizei uma combinação de técnicas para criar variações dos exemplos fornecidos. Aqui está o resultado:

"add article with title='The Great Expectations', year=2005, author='Charles Dickens'"",ADD,article,""{'title': 'The Great Expectations', 'year': '2005', 'author': 'Charles Dickens'}"",
""update student where name='Alexander', setting email='alexander@example.com'"",UPDATE,student,""{'email': 'alexander@example.com'},{'name': 'Alexander'}"",
""add product type=phone"",ADD,product,""{'type': 'phone'}"",
""get all music with artist='The Beatles'"",READ,music,""{}"",
""update car where license=2020, setting color='blue'"",UPDATE,car,""{'color': 'blue'},{'license': '2020'}"",
""add teacher with name='Sara Lee', department='Computer Science'"",ADD,teacher,""{'name': 'Sara Lee', 'department': 'Computer Science'}"",
""get all students where major='Environmental Science'"",READ,student,""{}"",
""update book where title='The Lord of the Flies', setting author='William Golding'"",UPDATE,book,""{'author': 'William Golding'},{'title': 'The Lord of the Flies'}"",
""add product with title='Samsung TV', type='electronic'"",ADD,product,""{'title': 'Samsung TV', 'type': 'electronic'}"",
""get all articles where year=2015"",READ,article,""{}"",
""update teacher where name='John Doe', setting department='Mathematics'"",UPDATE,teacher,""{'department': 'Mathematics'},{'name': 'John Doe'}"",
""add subject with name='Statistics', professor='Dr. Johnson'"",ADD,subject,""{'name': 'Statistics', 'professor': 'Dr. Johnson'}"",
""get all students where major='Astronomy'"",READ,student,""{}"",
""update music where title='Stairway to Heaven', setting genre='rock'"",UPDATE,music,""{'genre': 'rock'},{'title': 'Stairway to Heaven'}"",
...
...
